text.autoconfig.vorpal_enchantment.title: Vorpal Enchantment Config
text.autoconfig.vorpal_enchantment.optio: Chooses the chances for head drop per enchantment level. VANILLA_FRIENDLY has values 5%, 10%, 15%. SLIGHTLY_OP has values 5%, 15%, 25%. VERY_OP has 25%, 50%, 75%
Allows for axes to be enchanted with this enchantment
